div.p: Transaction boundary UPDATE urls + INSERT outbox single tx Redis DEL is post-commit, best-effort Redis failure: logged at Warn, 204 returned anyway

g.text: FindByCode(ctx, code)\nSELECT id, user_id, short_code\nFROM urls WHERE short_code=$1
UPDATE urls SET is_active=false\nWHERE short_code=$1 AND user_id=$2

INSERT INTO outbox
(event_type, payload)
VALUES ("url.deleted", $1)
RETURNING id, created_at
